      "text": "7. Swehtihts irr kas Zilweks/ \nkas us to KUNGS vataujahs/ \nun ka Zerriba tas KUNGS ir- \nraid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Jo tas buhs ka weens \nKohks pee Uhdens dehstihts/ kas \nfawas Saknes islaisch pee Up- \npes/ un ne juht kad Karstume \nnahk/ winan Lappas paleek sat- \ntas/ un Bulla Gadda wiꞥſch \nne behda/ un ne mittejahs Aug- \nfus nest.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Pahr wiſfahm Leetahm \nirr ta Sir̃s weena wiltiga/ un \nfamiſufi (Leeta/) kas warr to \nismanniht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Es tas KUNGS isman- \nnu to Sir̃di/ un pahrbandu tahs \nIhksts/ un dohinu ikkatram \npehz faween Zettecm/ pehz teem \nAugteem fawu Darbu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Jtt ka tas Putnis*/ kas \n(Pautus) dehj/ bet ne tsperre/ \ntapatt irr tas/ kas Baggatibu \nsakrahj/ bet ne ar Taisutbu/ fa- \nwas Dsihwibas Puſſinehrā \nbuhs winnam to atstaht/ un pa \nBallam weens Gekkis buht.\n* Eebr Wall: Kore.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Bet tas Krehslis tahs \nGohdtbas/ kas no Eṣahkuma \naugsts irraid/ irr muhsu sveh- \nta Weeta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Ak KUNGS! tu Isra- \netā Zerriba/ wiſti/ kas terwi at- \ntahj/ taps Kauna/ un manni\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Atkahpaji tafs Sennē raksti- \nti/ jo tee atstahj to KUNGS/ ta \ndsihwa Uhdens Awott.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Dsedina manni / ae \nKUNGS! tad tapfchu es dsee- \ndinahts/ atpesti manni/ tad tap- \nfchu es atpesihts/ jo tu eſti man- \nna teizaina Slawa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Rauqi/ tee fakka uhs \nmanni: Kur irr ta KUNGA \nWahrds: Laid jelle tas nahk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Tomehr es ne eſimu spee- \ndees/ ka es par Gannu buhtu/ \ntew pakkat eet/ ir Zilweku Beh- \ndu Deenas es ne eſimu eckahrojs/ \ntu finni to: Kas no mannas \nMuttes irr isqahjis/ tas irr ta- \nwā Breckshā (parei,) bijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Ne tehpi tu man par \nIstruhzinaschanu: Tu eſti mans \nPatweruins faunā Deena.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Laid manni Pakkatdsin- \nnejt Kauna tohp/ bet laid es ne \ntohpu Kaunā/ lai tee istruhzina- \nti tohp/ bet laid es ne tohpu is- \ntruhzinahts/ Weddi pahr teem \nNelatinibas Deenu/ un fatreez \ntohs ar divkahrtign Satreek- \nschanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Ta irr tas KUNGS uhs \nmanni fazzijs: Eij/ un stahwi \nto Lauschu Wahrtis/ zaur ko \ntee fehnini no Juha ee-eet/ un \nzaur ko tee tseet/ ir wiſtas Je- \nrusalennes Wahrtis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Un fakki uhs teem: Klau- \nfajt ta KUNGA Wahrdv/ juhs \nKehnint no Juha/ un wiſs \nJuha/ un wiſti juhs Jerusa- \nlemes Eedsihwotaji/ kas juhs\n"
    }
  ],
